{"tid":855663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暖氣排風口驚見一排怪黑毛　原來是上萬蜘蛛大軍！","createTime":"2018-10-10T07:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T08:08:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3c393c40f45bb82a843c0957a402ec5feedaebe0","tid":855663,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/15HinI9j6Xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F15HinI9j6Xk&d=ikXPlu%2B772jIrOP3wM5HehOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fb5aebb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/15HinI9j6Xk</a><br />\n<br />\n美國阿拉斯加州迪林厄姆（Dillingham）一名男子格拉斯（Thomas Glass），在屋外的暖氣排風口附近驚現一排毛叢叢詭異的黑毛，乍看之下就像一整排的毛髮，怎料格拉斯伸手撥過去時，數以千計蜘蛛隨即不斷跌下，才發現這些詭異的「毛髮」全都是蜘蛛的腳！<br />\n<br />\n拍下影片的湯瑪斯‧格拉斯住在阿拉斯加的迪林厄姆，隨即將影片分享至網絡，網民看完都覺得得毛骨悚然！當地因為已經入秋，天氣轉涼，這是俗稱「長腿叔叔」（Daddy Long Legs）的幽靈蜘蛛（學名：Pholcidae），常常都會聚成一團取暖，出現在當地居民的家中，當地都稱為「Dipdooly」，但從未見過這麼多數量聚集在一起。<br />\n<br />\n幽靈蜘蛛是一種在家中常會見到的生物，體型很小，體態纖細，特色是有細細長長的腿部，牠們常會用長腿把獵物抓住，還有一對毒牙，但是毒性並不強，還喜歡吃比自己體型大的蜘蛛，雖然沒有甚麼威脅性，但是可怕的細長腿快速移動起來，還是令人噁心！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/836932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F836932&d=ikXPlu%2B772jIrOP3wM5HehOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a406dfc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F836932&h=ec9e9fe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/836932</a><br />\n<br />\n點解條友可以仲咁淡定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b603481a9bf4938e9a633efe996c8c2dd76e0f43","tid":855663,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6315b9f44d1079a177f6535cd05cd3731d8cdf16","tid":855663,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply